name: A lot of things with the boring day

metadata.name: Take a little break with personal corner
metadata.description:
Digital painting create with procreate 

Every boring time She want to take a break from everything. Whether it's housework , people from real life and social media just for sit alone with herself 
She felt more relaxed by sitting on the floor. Put her head on the edge of bed. Smoking cigarettes as deep as possible then blew out the smoke…. Let many stories float and fade away with the smoke. Just that…! she felt a slight relief and freedom from the many things that were. Perhaps this was a small rest for drive her life to the next day
